<span id="freeTextContainer608394955161921722">I cannot say enough good things about this book. I was going to say this is a must read for all Muslims but another reader already used this title. However I think anyone who is looking for a self-help book should look at this book. From start to finish I was amazed by how much of the chapters of the book I could relate to myself. Reading this book and digesting the mental solutions and having unshakable faith as your foundation allow you to overcome any situation. A feeling of peace and tranqui</span>
  <span id="freeText608394955161921722" style="display:none">I cannot say enough good things about this book. I was going to say this is a must read for all Muslims but another reader already used this title. However I think anyone who is looking for a self-help book should look at this book. From start to finish I was amazed by how much of the chapters of the book I could relate to myself. Reading this book and digesting the mental solutions and having unshakable faith as your foundation allow you to overcome any situation. A feeling of peace and tranquillity came over me whilst reading this, I am sad I finished it. I have made a decision to read it a chapter at a time to my children. This book is the perfect blend of extracts of the Qur'an, stories of the Prophet (PBUH), his companions (PBUT), examples of problems and more importantly solutions to modern living.</span>
