  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/808365934" />
    <a title="Zoulfa Katouh" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/24044237-zoulfa-katouh"><img alt="Zoulfa Katouh" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1639585284p2/24044237.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/808365934?book_show_action=true">Jan 02, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Zoulfa Katouh" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Zoulfa Katouh" href="/user/show/24044237-zoulfa-katouh">Zoulfa Katouh</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer808365934" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7399135923992203856">Don&apos;t be Sad is the title of this book. Everything in this book just rises you up to the sky and makes you feel like Batman. It has been translated to English and was sold for millions of copies across the globe for those people who don&apos;t speak Arabic but need a self-empowering book that makes you believe that you can crush mountains and fly to the heavens. This is the book for you. I am actually not a huge fan of books like this for example The Secret but I am telling you this book... Oh my, oh</span>
  <span id="freeText7399135923992203856" style="display:none">Don't be Sad is the title of this book. Everything in this book just rises you up to the sky and makes you feel like Batman. It has been translated to English and was sold for millions of copies across the globe for those people who don't speak Arabic but need a self-empowering book that makes you believe that you can crush mountains and fly to the heavens. This is the book for you. I am actually not a huge fan of books like this for example The Secret but I am telling you this book... Oh my, oh my. No, this book is amazing. This book doesn't lie to you. It shows you the way to the person that you have been all along; which is Batman. Because who doesn't want to be Batman?</span>
